  "text": "• We apply our method to DNN model compression for a 32-layer ResNet model [CITATION_1] and fullresolution image compression using a variant of the compressive autoencoder proposed recently in [CITATION_2] . In both cases, we obtain performance competitive with the state-of-the-art, while making fewer model assumptions and significantly simplifying the training procedure compared to the original works [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
